Package ru.tinkoff.qa.neptune.core.api.steps

Class SequentialGetStepSupplier<T,R,M,P,THIS extends SequentialGetStepSupplier<T,R,M,P,THIS>>

java.lang.Object
ru.tinkoff.qa.neptune.core.api.steps.SequentialGetStepSupplier<T,R,M,P,THIS>
Type Parameters:
T - is a type of input value
R - is a type of returned value
M - is a type of mediator value is used to get the required result
P - is a type of value checked by a Predicate.
THIS - this is the self-type. It is used for the method chaining.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable, Supplier<Function<T,R>>, StepParameterPojo
Direct Known Subclasses:
SequentialGetStepSupplier.GetArrayChainedStepSupplier, SequentialGetStepSupplier.GetArrayStepSupplier, SequentialGetStepSupplier.GetListChainedStepSupplier, SequentialGetStepSupplier.GetListStepSupplier, SequentialGetStepSupplier.GetObjectChainedStepSupplier, SequentialGetStepSupplier.GetObjectFromArrayChainedStepSupplier, SequentialGetStepSupplier.GetObjectFromArrayStepSupplier, SequentialGetStepSupplier.GetObjectFromIterableChainedStepSupplier, SequentialGetStepSupplier.GetObjectFromIterableStepSupplier, SequentialGetStepSupplier.GetObjectStepSupplier, SequentialGetStepSupplier.GetSimpleStepSupplier
public abstract class SequentialGetStepSupplier<T,R,M,P,THIS extends SequentialGetStepSupplier<T,R,M,P,THIS>> extends Object implements Cloneable, Supplier<Function<T,R>>, StepParameterPojo
This class is designed to build and to supply sequential functions to get desired value. There are protected methods to be overridden/re-used as public when it is necessary.
